    </test>-->
    </tests>
    <help><![CDATA[    
Summary
=======

The pipeline aligns reads to the H37Rv reference using bowtie2, BWA or minimap2 and then calls variants using SAMtools. These variants are then compared to a drug-resistance database. 

We also predict the number of reads supporting drug resistance variants as an insight into hetero-resistance (not applicable for minION data).

Produces a JSON output file by default.

    ]]>    </help>
